<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>永旺 |一个思想的世界</title><link>https://aeon.co</link><description>Aeon 是一本关于思想和文化的杂志。我们发表深入的文章、精辟的文章以及原创和精选视频的组合——免费向所有人开放。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 28 Jun 2023 09:45:27 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>镜像双胞胎的神话</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/what-do-twin-studies-really-say-about-identity-and-genetics?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="镜像双胞胎的神话|永旺随笔" src="https://omicron.aeon.co/images/9be46917-3245-493c-8b17-72e9366cd230/show_essay-par192375.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;关于遗传性、自我以及先天与后天之间由来已久的争论，双胞胎的生活告诉我们什么？&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;——加文·埃文斯&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/what-do-twin-studies-really-say-about-identity-and-genetics?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jun 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/what-do-twin-studies-really-say-about-identity-and-genetics?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>世界还活着</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/the-grassroots-project-thats-restoring-an-endangered-hawaiian-ecosystem?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="奥拉卡霍努阿 |永旺视频" src="https://nu.aeon.co/images/75a6fa61-460c-46fe-8c90-65a3408ef765/show_ola-ka-honua-landscape-2.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;在一个充满希望的生态恢复故事中，认识一个社区在火山斜坡上恢复生机的森林&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/the-grassroots-project-thats-restoring-an-endangered-hawaiian-ecosystem?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Jun 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/the-grassroots-project-thats-restoring-an-endangered-hawaiian-ecosystem?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>成为你所希望的</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/what-can-augustine-of-hippos-philosophy-teach-us-about-hope?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="成为你所希望的那样 |永旺随笔" src="https://omicron.aeon.co/images/9021ae40-2612-427a-9ff7-b061ea8b89d2/show_esssay-v4-rtxd63ts.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;面对全球挑战，奥古斯丁在悲观主义的绝望和乐观主义的假设之间提供了一条出路&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——迈克尔·兰姆&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/what-can-augustine-of-hippos-philosophy-teach-us-about-hope?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Jun 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/what-can-augustine-of-hippos-philosophy-teach-us-about-hope?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>战争是怜悯和爱</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/what-crusaders-daggers-reveal-about-medieval-love-and-violence?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="战争是怜悯和爱 |永旺随笔" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/a5444139-94fb-415c-9a06-64c38b4b6dca/show_essay-final-akg5469206.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;骑士们参加十字军东征时携带的匕首帮助我们理解为什么他们认为圣战是一种爱的行为&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——威廉·切斯特·乔丹&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/what-crusaders-daggers-reveal-about-medieval-love-and-violence?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Jun 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/what-crusaders-daggers-reveal-about-medieval-love-and-violence?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>自由游泳者</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/one-story-in-a-sea-of-millions-of-swimming-from-china-to-freedom-in-hong-kong?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="自由泳者 |永旺视频" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/534796b5-c89a-4071-a9d8-27866c94f4c5/show_freedom-swimmer-landscape-2.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;一名“自由游泳者”从中国到香港的危险旅程——沿着200万人走过的路线&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/one-story-in-a-sea-of-millions-of-swimming-from-china-to-freedom-in-hong-kong?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Jun 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/one-story-in-a-sea-of-millions-of-swimming-from-china-to-freedom-in-hong-kong?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>重建多纳泰罗的雕塑</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/from-a-pencil-sketch-to-cherubs-dancing-in-stone-recreating-a-donatello-work?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="重建多纳泰罗的雕塑|永旺视频" src="https://alpha.aeon.co/images/7e6a33fe-7dd8-4f50-af16-c68f0a2c427d/show_recreating-donatellos-sculpture-landscape-4-v3.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;一位雕塑大师“啃咬”一块大理石，重现多纳泰罗浮雕中令人眼花缭乱的光影场景&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/from-a-pencil-sketch-to-cherubs-dancing-in-stone-recreating-a-donatello-work?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Jun 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/from-a-pencil-sketch-to-cherubs-dancing-in-stone-recreating-a-donatello-work?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>亚马逊儿童保育</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/why-runa-indigenous-people-find-natural-parenting-so-strange?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="亚马逊儿童保育|永旺随笔" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/eea1cd27-ead2-47aa-934a-f474cb9998f7/show_img_0124.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;在鲁纳人眼中，西方孩子在成长过程中被放纵、过度溺爱，无法面对外面的世界&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——弗朗西斯卡·梅泽扎纳&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/why-runa-indigenous-people-find-natural-parenting-so-strange?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Jun 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/why-runa-indigenous-people-find-natural-parenting-so-strange?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>某种亲密感</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/toby-ponders-the-inner-lives-of-the-sheep-that-roam-atop-his-parents-graves?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="某种亲密感 |永旺视频" src="https://nu.aeon.co/images/e72b0815-521f-486f-93f8-0a84d75cf268/show_some-kind-of-intimacy-landscape-1.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;对在什罗普郡墓地漫步的羊的失落和不可知的内心生活进行原创而深刻的思考&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/toby-ponders-the-inner-lives-of-the-sheep-that-roam-atop-his-parents-graves?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Jun 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/toby-ponders-the-inner-lives-of-the-sheep-that-roam-atop-his-parents-graves?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>这是蓝色食物</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/will-the-sustainable-food-of-the-future-come-from-the-blue?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="这是蓝色食物|永旺随笔" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/9cf2a585-efce-4be3-9737-60a6d34eb109/show_essay-final-gettyimages-944500300.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;考虑到社会和生态后果，海洋食物应该为数十亿人提供可持续的蛋白质&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——马杜拉·拉奥&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/will-the-sustainable-food-of-the-future-come-from-the-blue?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Jun 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/will-the-sustainable-food-of-the-future-come-from-the-blue?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>卡夫卡日记</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/on-the-space-between-waking-and-dreaming-in-kafkas-diaries?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="卡夫卡日记|永旺随笔" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/22148954-b027-4719-ae85-620253bb7df9/show_essay-v2-gettyimages-1425800389.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;白天，他是一名保险官员，晚上，他是一名不间断的、失眠的抄写员，记录着清醒和梦境之间的空间。&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;——罗斯·本杰明&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/on-the-space-between-waking-and-dreaming-in-kafkas-diaries?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Jun 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/on-the-space-between-waking-and-dreaming-in-kafkas-diaries?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item></channel></rss>